    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty ride, and she\u2019s ready for her next adventure! This car has been super reliable for me and is in really solid shape\u2014perfect for daily commutes or weekend road trips. It runs great and has been well-loved over the years. If you\u2019re looking for something dependable and fun to drive, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
